<p begin="23690000t" end="38590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="39700000t" end="72690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="73740000t" end="144390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="259590000t" end="302930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="303970000t" end="374960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="414740000t" end="498820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="516180000t" end="530850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="531860000t" end="565190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="566230000t" end="617880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="618950000t" end="667640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="668660000t" end="732940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="800130000t" end="830390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;第12話 愛意&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="840170000t" end="881810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;月,龍崎希望你協助我們調查&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="882880000t" end="904150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;如果你願意的話就立刻過來吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="911570000t" end="924880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;我知道了,爸爸&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="945610000t" end="976550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;我原本還打算先開口的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="977640000t" end="1000280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;想不到他倒先主動發出邀請&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1009000000t" end="1031980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;這樣我就可以瞭解&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;搜查總部的情報&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1033030000t" end="1058280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;又能正大光明&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;調查冒牌KIRA的事了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1066730000t" end="1085380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;我一定要搶先總部的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1086410000t" end="1119400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;調查清楚冒牌KIRA的底細&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1142470000t" end="1159760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;謝謝你,夜神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1160820000t" end="1171740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;不客氣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1172830000t" end="1201840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;我們想抓KIRA的心情&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是一樣的,流河&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1202860000t" end="1226520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;在這裡請稱呼我龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1237560000t" end="1257810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;我是松井&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我是相原&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1258920000t" end="1276890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;而我則是朝日&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1288620000t" end="1298290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;原來如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1303300000t" end="1330600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;那我就叫朝日月吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1331660000t" end="1347930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;那就拜託你了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1349010000t" end="1378020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;在這裡我會稱呼你為月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1387050000t" end="1403660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;雖然有點倉促&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1404730000t" end="1429980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;先請你看看關於KIRA的搜查情報&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1431090000t" end="1478420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;以及送到電視台裡&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;但尚末公開的帶子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1487810000t" end="1529450000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;禁止將資料帶出或寫下來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1530520000t" end="1541780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;我知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1542870000t" end="1555840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;那麼開始吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1589920000t" end="1599810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;月…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1630960000t" end="1641540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;那麼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1642640000t" end="1669940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;請隱瞞我們懷疑&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;有第二KIRA存在的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1671000000t" end="1709340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;請夜神月協助我們調查吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1710370000t" end="1719690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;可是&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1720710000t" end="1745960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;那我們會很難一起合作調查了啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1747070000t" end="1756960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;對啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1758080000t" end="1784360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;到底為什麼要讓他協助調查?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1785450000t" end="1846430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;別急,只是隱瞞到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;他看完帶子說出感想為止&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1851850000t" end="1884840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;月的推理能力非常出色&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1885880000t" end="1898850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;看完這卷帶子後&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1899890000t" end="1937200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;他可能也會推理出&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;或許有第二KIRA存在&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1941940000t" end="1962190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;不過第二KIRA存在的根據&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1963290000t" end="1979210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;只是因為他預告時殺的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1980310000t" end="2011940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;都是罪行很輕,KIRA不殺的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2013010000t" end="2035990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;這只有龍崎才推理得出來吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2043370000t" end="2058270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;不光是如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2063720000t" end="2089660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;根據我們以前的猜想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2090750000t" end="2117370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;KIRA殺人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;需要對方的樣貌以及姓名&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2126790000t" end="2175480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;可是當時宇生田&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;突然衝去電視台卻也被殺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2183510000t" end="2223780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;以及L一上電視就能殺他的語氣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2234890000t" end="2248200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;第二KIRA…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2249240000t" end="2272900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;或許只要看到樣貌就能殺人了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2290280000t" end="2325550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;先讓月看一下資料和帶子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2326650000t" end="2358620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;如果他推理出&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;可能有第二KIRA存在的話…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2359690000t" end="2388700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;月的嫌疑就大概可以消除了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2389720000t" end="2409630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;什麼意思啊,龍崎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2415740000t" end="2472400000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;KIRA絕對很想除掉&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;搜查總部的總指揮,L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2479810000t" end="2489700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;照這樣下去&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2490820000t" end="2543840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;我會照第二KIRA的要求&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;在三天後上電視並且被殺害&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2552550000t" end="2598510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;我認為KIRA&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;一定不會放過這個絕佳機會&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2599590000t" end="2637250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;那如果我兒子沒有推理出&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;可能有第二KIRA存在的話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2638300000t" end="2658890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;那他的嫌疑會不會加重?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2659990000t" end="2695940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;不,他的嫌疑還是不到5%&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2701690000t" end="2743670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;到時我會告訴他我關於第二KIRA的想法&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2744740000t" end="2759070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;請他協助調查&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2796120000t" end="2809430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;從以上事情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2810470000t" end="2846080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;就能相信我是真正的KIRA了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2854850000t" end="2869750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;看了這卷帶子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2870860000t" end="2893500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;讓人為他手法的粗劣感到想吐&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2894550000t" end="2917870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;是因為我才是KIRA的關係?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2918910000t" end="2948260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;他豈止是破壞了KIRA的形象…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2955610000t" end="2969600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;不過為什麼…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2970630000t" end="3004300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;竟然沒有人來講解這卷帶子的事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3005330000t" end="3015570000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;有點奇怪…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3025350000t" end="3037970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;但是無論如何&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3039030000t" end="3079300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;我還是別對這卷帶子發表意見吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3087750000t" end="3110050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;不管的話,L就會死了…&#x202c;</p>
