<p begin="9191840000t" end="9223120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle291">&#x202a;因為我是死神界裡極少數的…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9224210000t" end="9261520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle292">&#x202a;知道殺死死神方法的死神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9270260000t" end="9285840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle293">&#x202a;這就是原因吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9303290000t" end="9346290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle294">&#x202a;你是殺了別的死神&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;搶他的筆記本給我的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9353340000t" end="9386670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle295">&#x202a;不是的,並不是我殺的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9387710000t" end="9409320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle296">&#x202a;只不過碰巧有個死神死的時候&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9410400000t" end="9433040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle297">&#x202a;我剛好在場而已&#x202c;</p>
