<p begin="10325310000t" end="10357620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle314">&#x202a;突然有個男人從巷子旁出現&#x202c;</p>
